dssql:
SELECT a.AVATAR as AVATAR,a.CODBARRAS as CODBARRAS,a.DESCRIPCION as DESCRIPCION,a.IDXPROMPRODUCTO as IDXPROMPRODUCTO,a.NOTA as NOTA,a.PRECIOCOSTE as PRECIOCOSTE,a.PRECIOVENTA as PRECIOVENTA,a.PRODUCTO as PRODUCTO,a.REFINTERNA as REFINTERNA,a.STOCK as STOCK,a.STOCKMIN as STOCKMIN,a.TIPOPROD as TIPOPROD,a.IDPROMCATEGORIA0 as IDPROMCATEGORIA0,a.IDERPIMPUESTOS0 as IDERPIMPUESTOS0,a.IDPROVEEDOR0 as IDPROVEEDOR0,ab.TIPOIMPUESTO as TIPOIMPUESTO,ab.INCLUIDOPRECIO as INCLUIDOPRECIO,ab.IMPUESTO as IMPUESTO,ab.IVA as IVA,ab.ACTIVADO as ACTIVADO FROM PROMPRODUCTO a
 LEFT JOIN 
PROMCATEGORIA aa ON aa.IDXPROMCATEGORIA = a.IDPROMCATEGORIA0 LEFT JOIN 
ERPIMPUESTOS ab ON ab.IDXERPIMPUESTOS = a.IDERPIMPUESTOS0;
